_sText:
This is my second released map. I will be releasing a new beta map of this in time, along with my first map scout_b2b. 

This map has 32 Spawn points all together, 16 t, 16 ct. 

It can be used as a GG map if wanted its very fast paced.

I recommend 12 players, because I was testing it on my own dedicated server and it was comfortable not too laggy, but thats because I was also playing on the same machine.

Its a basic but fun map, enjoy. CC is appreciated ^-^
